# The core app builds with NO keys: iNaturalist, Open-Meteo (weather, elevation,
# soil moisture) and OpenStreetMap Overpass (canopy) are all public and keyless.
#
# Optional API keys enable extra features. Put them in `local.properties`
# (git-ignored) — NOT here, and NEVER commit a real key:
#
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...     # Claude-powered identification
#   GOOGLE_API_KEY=AIza...           # Google Geocoding / Elevation / Vision
#
# In CI, GOOGLE_API_KEY may instead be supplied as an environment variable.
# Restrict any Google key by API + Android app (package + SHA-1) in the
# Google Cloud console.
